<Routine Name="communicate_KMnO4" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[与2套KMnO4制备装置通讯。以及测试和活性炭西门子PLC的通讯]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[读写KMnO4制备装置参数]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(communicate_to_Micro850.DN)TON(communicate_to_Micro850,?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[读写KMnO4制备装置参数]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(communicate_to_Micro850.DN)XIO(KMnO4_solution_system_1.EN)MSG(KMnO4_solution_system_1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[读写KMnO4制备装置参数]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_1.DN) ,XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_1.ER) ]XIO(KMnO4_solution_system_2.EN)MSG(KMnO4_solution_system_2);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[读写KMnO4制备装置参数]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_2.DN) ,XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_2.ER) ]XIO(KMnO4_solution_system_3.EN)MSG(KMnO4_solution_system_3);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[读写KMnO4制备装置参数]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_3.DN) ,XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_3.ER) ]XIO(KMnO4_solution_system_4.EN)MSG(KMnO4_solution_system_4);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Modbus TCP Client AOI
AOI must be unconditionally True all the time
Multiple AOIs can be used to connect to multiple servers
One Server per Client AOI.
 Up to 5 transaction per Client AOI.
Use Rung Export/Import only, do not use Copy/Paste]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[raC_Opr_NetModbusTCPClient(VE,Client_01_EN,Client_01_Parameters,Client_01_Transactions,Client_01_Data,Client_01_MSG_Create,Client_01_MSG_Connect,Client_01_MSG_Read,Client_01_MSG_Write,Client_01_MSG_Delete,Client_01_MSG_SetSing);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="dosing_flow_set_KMnO4" Type="ST">
<Description>
<![CDATA[计算各数字泵投加流量：
1、手动设置时，以触摸屏设置流量为准；
2、自动控制时，以自动计算公式计算投加流量为准。
得出计算结果后，将流量传送到相关AO模块]]>
</Description>
<STContent>
<Line Number="0">
<![CDATA[(*1#数字泵流量计算*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="1">
<![CDATA[(*计算流量*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="2">
<![CDATA[dosing_flow_setting(]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="3">
<![CDATA[    dosing_flow_setting_5,]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="4">
<![CDATA[    KMnO4_control_auto_manual,(*控制状态：手动-0，自动-1*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="5">
<![CDATA[    KMnO4_dosing_mg_L_mixing_tank_1,(*KMnO4溶液投加率，原设计最大1mg/L*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="6">
<![CDATA[    P_KMnO4_1_flow_set,(*手动控制状态时，手动指定的投加流量L/h*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="7">
<![CDATA[    source_water_flow,(*源水流量m3/h*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="8">
<![CDATA[    flow_calculate_KMnO4_1,(*计算出来的投加量：手动时手动指定，自动时由计算得出*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="9">
<![CDATA[    KMnO4_concentration (*高锰酸钾溶液浓度，由高锰酸钾制备装置读取*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="10">
<![CDATA[    );]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="11">
<![CDATA[(*AO模块4-20mA输出*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="12">
<![CDATA[SCL(SCL_LP1010_AO_13);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="13">
<![CDATA[SCL_LP1010_AO_13.In:=flow_calculate_KMnO4_1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="14">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="15">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="16">
