<Routine Name="MainRoutine" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[主程序]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[设置NaClO系统4-20mA输入输出参数。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(analog_IO_setting_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[将I/O输入的数值，同步到系统变量，方便触摸屏及上位机读取]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(synchronize_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[将8个NaClO储罐当前液位，与液位过高报警值、液位过低报警值对照，如果液位过高、过低，则发出报警。
如果液位过高，则自动关闭进液阀。如果液位过低，则自动关闭出液位。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(tank_control_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[数字泵的启动/停止控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(pump_action_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[计算各数字泵投加流量，并传到相关AO模块输出。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(dosing_flow_set_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[NaClO浓液稀释程序，将10%的原液稀释为5%.]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(dilution_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[阀门动作控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(valve_action_NaClO,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[将计算得出的数字泵流量设置值传送到AO模块]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[MOV(SCL_LP400_AO_1.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch0Data)MOV(SCL_LP400_AO_2.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch1Data)MOV(SCL_LP400_AO_3.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch2Data)MOV(SCL_LP400_AO_4.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch3Data)MOV(SCL_LP400_AO_5.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch4Data)MOV(SCL_LP400_AO_6.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch5Data)MOV(SCL_LP1010_AO_7.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch6Data)MOV(SCL_LP1010_AO_8.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch7Data)MOV(SCL_LP1010_AO_9.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch8Data)MOV(SCL_LP1010_AO_10.Out,RemoteIO4:0:O.Ch9Data);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="pump_action_NaClO" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[控制数字泵的启动/停止]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#数字泵控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[pump_start_stop_NaClO(pump_action_NaClO_1,VE_NaClO45_open,VE_NaClO11_open,VE_NaClO12_open,VE_NaClO13_open,VE_NaClO14_open,VE_NaClO1_open,P_NaClO1_actuate,RemoteIO3:3:O.Data.0,VE_NaClO15_open,VE_NaClO16_open,VE_NaClO17_open,VE_NaClO18_open);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#数字泵控制]]>
