<Routine Name="tank_control_NaOH" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[储液罐液位控制流程。
液位过高过低报警。
液位过高时关闭进液阀，防止储液罐过满；
液位过低时关闭出液阀，防止计量泵空吸。]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#NaOH储罐液位]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_5,NaOH_tank_level_8LT05,NaOH_level_high_setting,NaOH_level_low_setting,NaOH_level_high_alarm_1,NaOH_level_low_alarm_1);]]>
