<Routine Name="tank_control_PAC" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[储液罐液位控制流程。
液位过高过低报警。
液位过高时关闭进液阀，防止储液罐过满；
液位过低时关闭出液阀，防止计量泵空吸。]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_1,PAC_tank_level_8LT01,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_1,PAC_level_low_alarm_1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#PAC池]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_2,PAC_tank_level_8LT02,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_2,PAC_level_low_alarm_2);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，远期规划，没有进液管和进液阀，进液阀输出有临时变量替代，实际安装后填入真正变量。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_3,PAC_tank_level_8LT03,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_3,PAC_level_low_alarm_3);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，远期规划，没有进液管和进液阀，进液阀输出有临时变量替代，实际安装后填入真正变量。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_4,PAC_tank_level_8LT04,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_4,PAC_level_low_alarm_4);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="valve_action_PAC" Type="ST">
<Description>
<![CDATA[阀门动作的控制分为分类：
1、普通电动阀可以自由动作；
2、泵出口阀需要与泵联动；
3、储罐进出口阀与储罐液位联动。]]>
</Description>
<STContent>
<Line Number="0">
<![CDATA[(*阀门动作的控制分为分类：*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="1">
<![CDATA[(*1、普通电动阀可以自由动作；*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="2">
<![CDATA[(*2、泵出口阀需要与泵联动；*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="3">
<![CDATA[(*3、储罐进出口阀与储罐液位联动。*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="4">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="5">
<![CDATA[(*1、普通电动阀控制*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="6">
<![CDATA[RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.18:=VE_PAC_11_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="7">
<![CDATA[RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.19:=VE_PAC_12_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="8">
<![CDATA[RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.20:=VE_PAC_13_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="9">
<![CDATA[RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.21:=VE_PAC_14_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="10">
<![CDATA[RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.22:=VE_PAC_15_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="11">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="12">
<![CDATA[(*2、泵出口阀控制*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="13">
<![CDATA[(*数字泵启动时，泵出口阀由数字泵控制程序控制，此时泵出口阀必须开启*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="14">
<![CDATA[(*1#泵的出口阀*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="15">
<![CDATA[if RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.4 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="16">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.8:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="17">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="18">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.8:=VE_PAC_01_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="19">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="20">
<![CDATA[(*2#泵的出口阀*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="21">
<![CDATA[if RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.5 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="22">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.9:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="23">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="24">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.9:=VE_PAC_02_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="25">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="26">
<![CDATA[(*3#泵的出口阀*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="27">
<![CDATA[if RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.6 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="28">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.10:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="29">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="30">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.10:=VE_PAC_03_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="31">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="32">
<![CDATA[(*4#泵的出口阀*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="33">
<![CDATA[if RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.7 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="34">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.11:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="35">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="36">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.11:=VE_PAC_04_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="37">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="38">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="39">
<![CDATA[(*3、储罐进出口阀控制*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="40">
<![CDATA[(*进口阀控制*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="41">
<![CDATA[(*1#池的入口阀*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="42">
<![CDATA[if PAC_level_high_alarm_1 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="43">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.12:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="44">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="45">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.12:=VE_PAC_05_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="46">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="47">
<![CDATA[(*2#池的入口阀*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="48">
<![CDATA[if PAC_level_high_alarm_2 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="49">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.13:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="50">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="51">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.13:=VE_PAC_06_actuate;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="52">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="53">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="54">
<![CDATA[(*出口阀控制*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="55">
<![CDATA[(*1#池的出口阀*)]]>
